text: Hey! My client runs the bot on Australian VPS and it works well. But then he decided to change the server (location - UK) and started getting an error 'MULTIPLE_USERS_WITH_SAME_CREDENTIAL'. He runs only 1 bot simultaneously, not both servers. Interactive login. Are there any methods to 'reset' the session? Or what would you recommend to fix this error? The goal is to just run it on the UK server.
